Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.78,0:00:15.49,Opening,,0,0,0,,My right hand holds a bowl of gold,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.49,0:00:19.79,Opening,,0,0,0,,And my left holds one of silver.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.79,0:00:24.46,Opening,,0,0,0,,Never one without the other,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.46,0:00:37.65,Opening,,0,0,0,,Two unseen bowls for each of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.65,0:00:45.98,Opening,,0,0,0,,The golden one is filled with joy,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.98,0:00:53.40,Opening,,0,0,0,,shining warmly.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.40,0:00:57.99,Opening,,0,0,0,,Since we met, my golden bowl
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.99,0:01:05.21,Opening,,0,0,0,,cannot hold all my happiness and love.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.83,0:01:15.35,Opening,,0,0,0,,Golden joy, silver sadness,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.35,0:01:22.70,Opening,,0,0,0,,I would leave my past behind...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.70,0:01:27.43,Opening,,0,0,0,,For you, for the sake of love,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.43,0:01:34.37,Opening,,0,0,0,,I would empty the bowls of my past.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.12,0:02:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,My Dear Brother, I'm finally here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.01,0:02:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,At your school, for the Gakuin University Fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.46,0:02:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So many people!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.56,0:02:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! University fairs are so different from the high school ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.07,0:02:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,This is so exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.01,0:02:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Mariko-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.97,0:02:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.21,0:02:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so tense, especially your shoulders.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.02,0:02:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And why not, after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.55,0:02:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Protecting you two from all the males here is a grave responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.05,0:02:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.56,0:03:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What? But... wait a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.53,0:03:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't remember anyone asking her for protection!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.97,0:03:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.10,0:03:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,There! They're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.01,0:03:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi! Glad you're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.64,0:03:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm very grateful that you sent me an invitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.58,0:03:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,My pleasure! Thanks for coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.65,0:03:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,May I present my friends, Shinobu Mariko-san and Arikura Tomoko-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.00,0:03:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Henmi Takehiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.92,0:03:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,How do... ...you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.35,0:03:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi Henmi-sensei, it's been a long time!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.93,0:03:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.65,0:03:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I was in the same cram school with Nanako.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.33,0:03:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The name is Arikura.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.54,0:03:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! It's you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.74,0:03:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, we tagged along today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.30,0:03:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, the more the merrier!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.63,0:03:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... This... this is my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.08,0:03:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Ichinomiya Takashi. Glad to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.82,0:03:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You said... Ichinomiya?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.55,0:04:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,So you are...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.55,0:04:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. He's Miya-sama's brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.09,0:04:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.89,0:04:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.68,0:04:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand you all attend Seiran with my sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.68,0:04:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Glad you came. Pleased to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.23,0:04:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a typical "guy" strategy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.60,0:04:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,They pretend to shake hands for "friendship",
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.45,0:04:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,...but they're probably already planning their next move!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.08,0:04:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.24,0:04:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if he's Miya-sama's brother, he's still a guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.25,0:04:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So don't let down your guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.46,0:04:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Bleh!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.79,0:04:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,21. The University Fair
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.30,0:04:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,How about it? Where shall we start?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.00,0:04:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,How about the movies?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.34,0:04:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Our university's movie study-group is highly regarded.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.34,0:04:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.08,0:04:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! I want to see that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.75,0:05:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! Movies, of all things!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.28,0:05:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,How obvious can you get?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.89,0:05:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Movies, as you well know, are shown in dark rooms!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.23,0:05:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And now for some magic with cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.96,0:05:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a gorgeous lady in our midst, with a diamond ring,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.17,0:05:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,...my heart is on fire. Our love is in spades!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.88,0:05:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch out, both of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.11,0:05:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.60,0:05:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Using this type of comedy...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.38,0:05:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,...it's an attempt to put us at ease.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.98,0:05:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That should be obvious to anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.79,0:05:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Here is a 140 to 1 scale model of Neuschwanstein Castle in Germany.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.57,0:05:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well made.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.03,0:05:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Rudreich the 2nd had it built in the 17th century.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.73,0:05:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It took him 17 years...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.75,0:05:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What an amateur you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.40,0:05:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,...showing off knowledge, using a woman's feelings of inferiority...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.47,0:05:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,...anyone can see through that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.75,0:06:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,A Haunted House! It looks like fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.06,0:06:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,A Haunted house?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.97,0:06:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't been in one since Junior High.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.49,0:06:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall we try it? It'll bring back memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.44,0:06:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! I love these things!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.85,0:06:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinobu-san, don't you dare oppose this one!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.88,0:06:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't oppose it, but, let's separate into two groups...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.57,0:06:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Males go with males and females go with females.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.85,0:06:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,This is sort of scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.38,0:06:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why we should have had them come with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.05,0:06:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.52,0:06:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,They'd only invite girls into a place like this if they had ulterior motives.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.84,0:06:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Ulterior motives?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.59,0:06:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What sort of "ulterior motive"?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.93,0:07:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd rather hug the ghost than them, in this panic and confusion...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.14,0:07:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,This is just an old familiar trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.94,0:07:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So what do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.87,0:07:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.29,0:07:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.76,0:07:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.81,0:07:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Aieeeee!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.90,0:07:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never been so humiliated in my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.97,0:07:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Humiliated? Wasn't it you that ran into me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.89,0:07:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't have been there!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.00,0:07:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And look, why do you have to sit so close to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.32,0:07:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Move further away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.11,0:07:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.65,0:07:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Further!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.61,0:07:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Ma-am...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.65,0:07:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Further!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.86,0:07:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Mariko-san! Please behave yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.33,0:08:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.50,0:08:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.75,0:08:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Your vigilance in this respect is truly admirable,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.41,0:08:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,...but come on, let's relax and have some fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.48,0:08:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,This is our University Fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.80,0:08:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't come here to have fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.22,0:08:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I came here to protect Nanako-san and Tomoko-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.23,0:08:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm completely at a loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.35,0:08:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you hate men so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.96,0:08:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,They are selfish... dirty... and the cruelest creatures on earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.65,0:08:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you say all men are like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.17,0:08:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you say they're not!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.50,0:08:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I can certainly say that I', not!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.70,0:08:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true! Men are all talk but no deed!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.38,0:08:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Henmi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.97,0:09:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time to meet and be heard!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.86,0:09:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Assemble with us to defend our cultural heritage.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.79,0:09:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Exercise your constitutional right to free speech!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.45,0:09:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't it seem like there are more people here, now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.91,0:09:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,At 2 o'clock there's a concert in the gym.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.48,0:09:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an amateur band, and fairly popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.88,0:09:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,A rock group. Do you want to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.67,0:09:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.29,0:09:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I know them! They're "Mercury"! I love them!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.70,0:09:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like a balloon?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.63,0:09:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,No. Balloons always burst and too soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.24,0:09:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you dislike things that don't last?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.24,0:09:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a delicate one, aren't you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.40,0:09:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're pretentious.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.98,0:09:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.62,0:10:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.85,0:10:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.59,0:10:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to them?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.33,0:10:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,They're lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.25,0:10:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if Mariko-san is okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.96,0:10:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll be okay. She's with Ichinomiya-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.16,0:10:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we can have some fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.67,0:10:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.40,0:10:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! Slow down!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.87,0:10:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you please stop following me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.89,0:10:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't leave you alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.14,0:10:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm responsible for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.64,0:10:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Until I find Henmi and the others, I'm your bodyguard!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.19,0:10:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have nothing of the sort!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.19,0:10:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,If not a bodyguard, then, consider me a "practice date".
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.89,0:10:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You make my flesh crawl.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.41,0:10:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,All right then, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.30,0:10:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, where were you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.04,0:10:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,To the public address booth. I'll have them page Nanako-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.92,0:10:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Not in this auxiliary buildings. That would be in the main building.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.80,0:10:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.64,0:11:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides... during school fairs, they don't make announcements.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.70,0:11:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay at least one meter away from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.18,0:11:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That won't be easy...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.10,0:12:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Any further away from you, and we might be separated too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.84,0:12:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,If we get separated, that'll suit me fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.58,0:12:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.47,0:12:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Ichinomiya-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.55,0:12:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.53,0:12:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,A friend. In my class.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.72,0:12:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.52,0:12:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Ichinomiya-sempai!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.33,0:12:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you try shooting? I'll give you a discount.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.93,0:12:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure. But later.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.07,0:12:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,She's in my ski club.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.07,0:12:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, it's been a while!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.75,0:12:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi! How have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.04,0:12:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And this lovely lady... your girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.32,0:12:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We're complete strangers.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.15,0:12:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.68,0:12:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.76,0:12:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You certainly have a lot of female friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.39,0:13:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.34,0:13:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess... you know, being a university student...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.64,0:13:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,All men are like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.79,0:13:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,They can't be satisfied with just one girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.06,0:13:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You're prejudiced.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.64,0:13:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd be very happy with one girl. But I need to have friends also.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.12,0:13:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever you're male or female, try to make a friend whenever you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.53,0:13:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't presume to give me advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.24,0:13:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.97,0:13:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.33,0:13:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What else looks interesting?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.33,0:13:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,We've seen most of them...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.09,0:13:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We had so much fun! Really!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.88,0:13:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! This was our first university fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.08,0:13:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been so exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.93,0:13:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,In three years, you may be the ones putting on a fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.33,0:13:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.82,0:13:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that too far ahead to think about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.62,0:14:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. It's just too distant in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.78,0:14:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow... three years!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.83,0:14:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I could be walking hand in hand with my boyfriend...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.17,0:14:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, do you have a girlfriend, Henmi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.49,0:14:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.18,0:14:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I must admit, it hadn't occurred to me before...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.22,0:14:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,...but it wouldn't surprise me if my Brother has a girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.72,0:14:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm sorry! Was that an improper question?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.51,0:14:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,No girlfriend. Not right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.59,0:14:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Satisfied?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.06,0:14:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Well! You dodged that one! A different subject, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.87,0:14:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you come to select this university?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.27,0:14:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, now... in order to answer that question...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.21,0:14:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I gave you an easy one, this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.68,0:14:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, my dear Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.20,0:14:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I really don't know anything about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.09,0:15:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I wrote you so many long letters,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.40,0:15:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,...they must've been a burden to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.23,0:15:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But I've only been thinking of myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.83,0:15:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You're such a considerate and gentle person.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.06,0:15:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Taking advantage of your generosity... is not very nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.59,0:15:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's wrong of me, it really is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.69,0:15:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Cotton candy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.53,0:15:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.49,0:15:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go get some for you, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.59,0:15:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Thinking about something?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.46,0:15:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.53,0:15:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been so quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.13,0:15:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! That was just...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.80,0:15:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just starting to worry a bit...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.23,0:15:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Worry?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.74,0:15:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes... It was selfish of me to make you be my "Brother".
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.54,0:16:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be terribly busy with your studies, and everything else...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.28,0:16:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And so I'm worried...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.69,0:16:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,...that I've become a burden to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.15,0:16:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,A burden? I never thought of it that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.23,0:16:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Reading your letters reminds me of my own high school days.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.87,0:16:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Back then, the most trivial things could make me happy or angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.17,0:16:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Your letters bring all those feelings back to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.30,0:16:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, I look forward to checking my mailbox.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.26,0:16:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.65,0:16:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Really! It's true. Speaking of which...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.27,0:16:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.52,0:16:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,When's the next letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.75,0:16:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Where could they have gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.91,0:16:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,In a crowd like this, it'll be next to impossible to find them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.61,0:17:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like looking for a contact lens in a swimming pool.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.02,0:17:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's okay. We can always just wait for them at the main gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.82,0:17:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Look over here... Don't girls love this sort of things?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.22,0:17:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.10,0:17:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? It looks fun! Whether it's true or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.65,0:17:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But... I guess I'll try it anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.78,0:17:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You are strong-willed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.65,0:17:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it strong will, or just a "hard-head"?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.55,0:17:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.05,0:17:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You are bright, and you have good luck with money.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.88,0:17:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Except...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.67,0:17:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Except?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.06,0:17:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Except there's a problem related to your family...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.60,0:18:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Your parents are...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.14,0:18:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.87,0:18:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you... What do you know about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.77,0:18:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had enough of this nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.10,0:18:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.68,0:18:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,300 Yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.62,0:18:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey girl! You alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.89,0:18:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,How'd you like us to show you around?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.36,0:18:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,We're students here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.70,0:18:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get uppity, now. Get that serious look off your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.44,0:18:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, hey... there's a disco party at 5 o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.01,0:18:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We wanted to go, 'cept for being just 2 guys alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.51,0:18:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, listen here, wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.23,0:18:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.92,0:18:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.72,0:18:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't stand to be touched by your filthy hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.48,0:18:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate scum like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.33,0:19:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop following me! Get lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.32,0:19:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Get away from me right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.62,0:19:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I'm a failure as a bodyguard.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.62,0:19:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall we go? Everyone's staring.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.39,0:19:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave yourself, if you're so concerned about what they think.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.70,0:19:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Or you can just stay and watch me like them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.44,0:19:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, I understand. I'll wait until you're ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.92,0:20:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go. This is foolish.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.21,0:20:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey Henmi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.68,0:20:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Mariko-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.78,0:20:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I figured you'd be here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.81,0:20:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes... when lost, one should backtrack to the point of origin.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.25,0:20:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad. I was worried that we'd never find you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.71,0:20:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't believe what happened... it was terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.80,0:20:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Since we're finally back together, why don't we go for some coffee?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.83,0:20:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, let's!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.70,0:20:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be absurd!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.41,0:20:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time to go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.56,0:20:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What... Why can't we all have coffee?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.37,0:20:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,But don't you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.95,0:20:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,While we're drinking coffee, the sun will set!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.02,0:21:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Before we know it, it'll be totally dark!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.06,0:21:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,No it won't!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.45,0:21:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes it will!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.88,0:21:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go! Good bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.86,0:21:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Mariko-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.94,0:21:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a second! Shinobu-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.79,0:21:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Oops! Thank you very much for today!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.11,0:21:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You're welcome...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.83,0:21:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.48,0:21:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You're too fast! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.34,0:21:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I won't wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.89,0:21:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't know how men change into dangerous wolves after dark!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.72,0:21:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What a girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.48,0:21:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It must've been terrible being stuck with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.09,0:21:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.75,0:21:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I kind of liked it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.86,0:21:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.89,0:21:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I got to liking her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.08,0:21:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you Nanako!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.44,0:21:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of you I had such a good time!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.00,0:21:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.83,0:22:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! Because you became a sister of Henmi-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.31,0:22:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.76,0:22:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,But, Mariko-san was so uptight today.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.55,0:22:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Her man-hating thing seems a little sick... I wonder why she does that...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.39,0:22:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, there's a problem. A complex problem in her family.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.75,0:22:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.03,0:22:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.81,0:22:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The time flies when we're having fun,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.88,0:22:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,...but tomorrow, it's back to school again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.75,0:22:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,...or so it seems...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.71,0:22:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,This is heavy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.32,0:22:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.49,0:22:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Apple tea, your favorite.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.55,0:22:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.29,0:22:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,How was it, at the university?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.39,0:22:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I had fun! But there were so many people.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.57,0:22:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a little overwhelming.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.65,0:23:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Well. You're lucky you had someone to show you around.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.35,0:23:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.98,0:23:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So... take your bath now.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.00,0:23:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.52,0:23:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother, Dear Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.26,0:23:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,For the warmth of your company,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.40,0:23:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,...and this wonderful, gentle day together,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.45,0:23:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,...I would like to express my sincere gratitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.34,0:23:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.01,0:24:14.21,Ending,,0,0,0,,I dreamed I was chasing a rainbow...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.21,0:24:19.68,Ending,,0,0,0,,Then the rainbow I was chasing was you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.15,0:24:25.29,Ending,,0,0,0,,Before, I had no strength, no will.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.29,0:24:30.76,Ending,,0,0,0,,But now because of you, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.50,0:24:37.04,Ending,,0,0,0,,Feelings of love, like raindrops
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.04,0:24:42.51,Ending,,0,0,0,,Come pouring from the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.51,0:24:45.24,Ending,,0,0,0,,This is surely a game
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.24,0:24:48.05,Ending,,0,0,0,,Of some mischievous fairy...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.05,0:24:50.45,Ending,,0,0,0,,Always dancing,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.45,0:24:55.72,Ending,,0,0,0,,Always capricious...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.56,0:25:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Visiting Fukiko's vacation home to help prepare for Fukiko's birthday party,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.11,0:25:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,...she is stunned to overhear Fukiko's mournful suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.82,0:25:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The following day, before Nanako's eyes, Fukiko jumps into the lake.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.25,0:25:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Next episode: A Summer's Serenade
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.58,0:25:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother, Dear Brother... There is no end to my tears...
